# ── NEVER commit real financial data ──────────────────────────────
# If you clone this and run the prompt on your own statements, these
# patterns keep your raw exports and any pipeline output that may hold
# real numbers out of git. The demo dashboard (public/dashboard.html)
# is fictional and is intentionally committed.
*.csv
*.xls
*.xlsx
*.ofx
*.qfx
*.qbo
/data/
raw/
transactions*.json
classified*.json
dashboard_data*.json
audit_metrics*.json
audit_findings*.json
uncategorized*.json
tail_rules*.json
subs_extra*.json
Financial-Almanac.html

# ── High-res screenshot sources (optimized copies live in public/) ─
docs/screenshots/

